						<div class="postbody">I didn't check your code, but this doc contains info about how to set the scrolling to any coordinates midscreen:
<br />
<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://nesdev.com/2C02%20technical%20reference.TXT">http://nesdev.com/2C02%20techn ... erence.TXT</a><!-- m -->
<br />
<br />It's in the end of the doc, under "establishing full split screen scrolls mid-frame". Same stuff, in different format, is also in <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://nesdev.com/loopyppu.zip">http://nesdev.com/loopyppu.zip</a><!-- m --></div>

					
