						<div class="postbody">sampsonk, I hadn't noticed that your name table is at the bottom of the screen. I'm not sure why your code didn't work, as 2 writes to $2006 should be enough to point to the top of your status bar... theoretically, there is no need for the complex $2006/$2005/$2005/$2006 setup. You should clear the X scroll through $2005 though, or the status bar could shift sideways by up to 7 pixels.
<br />
<br />Maybe this is a timing issue... try adding a few NOPs before the writes to $2006 so see if anything changes. Also make sure that all your writes to $2005 and $2006 are made in pairs, so that the latch that selects between first and second writes isn't left in the wrong state.</div>

