					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Ok, so I've traced through SMB3's interrupt code:
<br />It writes $00 to $2006 4 times, and then $0B, $00 to $2006, reads $2007 once, and then does a bunch of bankswitching code, ending with writing $00 to $2005, and then rewriting the screen's y-scrolling coordinate to $2005.</div>

					
